{"name": "set-proxy", "metadata": {"name": "set_proxy", "version": "0.1.1", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests"], "summary": "a network checker and proxy setter", "upload_time": 1735699967}, "documentation": ["# set_proxy\n\n\u4e00\u4e2a\u7b80\u5355\u7684 Python \u5de5\u5177\uff0c\u7528\u4e8e\u8bbe\u7f6e\u548c\u7ba1\u7406\u7cfb\u7edf\u4ee3\u7406\u3002\n\n## \u529f\u80fd\u7279\u70b9\n\n- \u5feb\u901f\u8bbe\u7f6e\u7cfb\u7edf\u4ee3\u7406\n- \u652f\u6301 HTTP \u548c HTTPS \u4ee3\u7406\n- \u8de8\u5e73\u53f0\u652f\u6301\uff08Windows\u3001macOS\u3001Linux\uff09\n\n## \u5b89\u88c5\n\n```bash\npip install set-proxy\n```\n\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\n\n```python\nfrom set_proxy import set_proxy\n\n# \u8bbe\u7f6e\u4ee3\u7406\nset_proxy(\"http://127.0.0.1:7890\")\n\n# \u6e05\u9664\u4ee3\u7406\nset_proxy(None)\n\n# \u68c0\u67e5 Google \u8fde\u63a5\u72b6\u6001\nfrom set_proxy import check_google\n\n# \u9ed8\u8ba4\u68c0\u67e5 https://www.google.com\ncheck_google()\n\n# \u6216\u8005\u6307\u5b9a\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49 URL\ncheck_google(\"https://www.google.com/search\")\n```\n\n## \u8d21\u732e\n\n\u6b22\u8fce\u63d0\u4ea4 Issue \u548c Pull Request\uff01\n\n## \u53d1\u5e03\u6d41\u7a0b\n\n\u672c\u9879\u76ee\u4f7f\u7528 GitHub Actions \u81ea\u52a8\u53d1\u5e03\u5230 PyPI\u3002\u53d1\u5e03\u65b0\u7248\u672c\u7684\u6b65\u9aa4\u5982\u4e0b\uff1a\n\n1. \u66f4\u65b0\u7248\u672c\u53f7\uff08\u5728 pyproject.toml \u4e2d\u624b\u52a8\u4fee\u6539\u7248\u672c\u53f7\uff09\uff1a\n\n   ```toml\n   [project]\n   name = \"set-proxy\"\n   version = \"0.1.0\"  # \u4fee\u6539\u8fd9\u91cc\u7684\u7248\u672c\u53f7\n   # ...\n   ```\n\n2. \u63d0\u4ea4\u66f4\u6539\uff1a\n\n   ```bash\n   git add pyproject.toml\n   git commit -m \"bump: \u7248\u672c\u66f4\u65b0\u5230 0.1.0\"\n   ```\n\n3. \u521b\u5efa\u6807\u7b7e\uff1a\n\n   ```bash\n   git tag v0.1.0  # \u4f7f\u7528\u5bf9\u5e94\u7684\u7248\u672c\u53f7\n   ```\n\n4. \u63a8\u9001\u66f4\u6539\u548c\u6807\u7b7e\uff1a\n\n   ```bash\n   git push\n   git push --tags\n   ```\n\n\u63a8\u9001\u6807\u7b7e\u540e\uff0cGitHub Actions \u5c06\u81ea\u52a8\u6784\u5efa\u5e76\u53d1\u5e03\u5305\u5230 PyPI\u3002\n\n## \u8bb8\u53ef\u8bc1\n\nMIT License\n"], "modules": [{"name": "set_proxy", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "set_proxy.set_socks", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "port", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "set_proxy.set_http_proxy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "port", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "set_proxy.check_link", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "set_proxy.check_hf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "set_proxy.check_baidu", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "set_proxy.check_google", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "set_proxy.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}]}